File-Size version 0.04
======================

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  File::Find
  Cwd
  Number::Bytes::Human

